renheit-182）封面。信用：出版" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Mark-Hoppus-Fahrenheit-182-book-cover.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Mark-Hoppus-Fahrenheit-182-book-cover.-Credit-PRESS-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Mark-Hoppus-Fahrenheit-182-book-cover.-Credit-PRESS-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Mark-Hoppus-Fahrenheit-182-book-cover.-Credit-PRESS-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Mark-Hoppus-Fahrenheit-182-book-cover.-Credit-PRESS-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Mark-Hoppus-Fahrenheit-182-book-cover.-Credit-PRESS-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/Blink-182">Blink 182</a>的<a href="/artists/Mark-Hoppus">马克·霍普斯（Mark Hoppus）</a>宣布了“与马克·霍普斯（Mark Hoppus）的夜晚”，这是他在伦敦发行的“独家”活动。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong> <strong><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/blink-182-one-more-time-review-lyrics-tracklist-3517188">Blink-182  - “再一次”评论：令人惊讶的触摸聚会</a></strong></li></ul><p>霍普斯（Hoppus）的回忆录<em>《华氏回忆录182》</em> （ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/blink-182s-mark-hoppus-announces-memoir-fahrenheit-182-3794239">以前是去年9月宣布的</a>）将介入他在Blink-182的时代（包括他们的形成和分手），以及他在焦虑，自杀念头和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mark-hoppus-shares-insight-into-beginning-of-cancer-diagnosis-3029532">癌症诊断方面</a>的挣扎。</p><p>他在当时的宣传<a href="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C_--BVmvTjX/?hl=en-gb" target="_blank" rel="noopener">视频</a>中说：“这种狗屎变黑了。”他在一次宣传视频中还补充说，该项目是“音乐回忆录的组合遇到医疗旅程”。该书定于4月8日发行，可以<a href="https://www.waterstones.com/book/fahrenheit-182/mark-hoppus/9781408724552" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>预订。</p><p>现在，这位标志性的贝斯手宣布了5月5日在伦敦的萨沃伊剧院（Savoy Theatre）举行的独家活动，名为“与马克·霍普斯（Mark Hoppus）的夜晚”。该活动将是Hoppus和特别嘉宾之间进行的调节。该活动的门票将包括<em>华氏182年</em>的副本（Sphere提供的25英镑价值）。通用门票销售将于星期五（3月14日）上午10点开始。访问<a href="https://www.atgtickets.com/shows/an-evening-with-mark-hoppus-and-all-things-fahrenheit-182/savoy-theatre/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">这里</a>购买。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DHERF3GvT40/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,