uploads/2025/03/Damiano-David.-Credit-Damon-Baker-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Damiano-David.-Credit-Damon-Baker-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Damiano-David.-Credit-Damon-Baker-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Damiano-David.-Credit-Damon-Baker-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Damiano-David.-Credit-Damon-Baker-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/Maneskin">Måneskin</a>的<a href="/artists/Damiano-David">Damiano David</a>宣布了他的首张个人专辑“ Funny Little Fears”的发行日期。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/maneskin-cover-interview-2022-supermodel-3233987">封面上的Måneskin：“没有人保持Rock&#39;n&#39;n&#39;Roll活着 - 这是不可能杀死的</a></strong></li></ul><p>意大利歌手兼作曲家和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/italian-eurovision-winners-maneskin-drugs-new-music-tour-james-newman-interview-2949022">Eurovision获奖乐队</a>的Solo专辑的主持人将于5月16日通过Italy / Arista发行。它将以他的首张独奏单曲“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-damiano-davids-uplifting-new-single-born-with-a-broken-heart-3806083">Born with the Heart</a> ”， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/labrinth">Labrinth</a>生产的“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/maneskin-damiano-david-inteview-silverlines-solo-album-band-future-3797604">Silverlines</a> ”和他的最新发行“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/maneskins-damiano-david-shares-new-solo-single-next-summer-3842457">明年夏天</a>”为特色。</p><p> “有趣的小恐惧”将以数字方式和各种物理格式（例如乙烯基和CD）提供。 LP由14条轨道组成，标志着新闻稿所描述的“达米亚诺职业和艺术性的大胆而挑衅的新篇章”。</p><p>它有望看到大卫“打破了声音和抒情的期望模式，违抗流派边界，并在面对恐惧时勇敢地走在自己思想的范围内。” </p><figure id="attachment_3845422" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3845422" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3845422" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Damiano-David-Funny-Little-Fears-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="达米亚诺·戴维（Damiano David）的“有趣的小恐惧”专辑艺术品。信用：出版" width="2000" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Damiano-David-Funny-Little-Fears-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Damiano-David-Funny-Little-Fears-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Damiano-David-Funny-Little-Fears-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Damiano-David-Funny-Little-Fears-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Damiano-David-Funny-Little-Fears-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Damiano-David-Funny-Little-Fears-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1392x1392.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Damiano-David-Funny-Little-Fears-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3845422" class="wp-caption-text">达米亚诺·戴维（Damiano David）的“有趣的小恐惧”专辑艺术品。信用：出版</figcaption></figure><h2><strong>“有趣的小恐惧”曲目清单是</strong></h2><p><strong>1。“声音”</strong><br /> <strong>2。“明年夏天”</strong><br /> <strong>3。&#39;僵尸女士&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>4。“瘀伤”</strong><br /> <strong>5。“生病”</strong><br /> <strong>6。&#39;天使&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>7。&#39;探戈&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>8。“天生有伤心的心”</strong><br /> <strong>9。“橘子”</strong><br /> <strong>10。“火星”</strong><br /> <strong>11。“第一次”</strong><br /> <strong>12。“完美的生活”</strong><br /> <strong>13。“银线”</strong><br /> <strong>14。“孤独（没人理解我）”</strong></p><p> David在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/maneskin-damiano-david-inteview-silverlines-solo-album-band-future-3797604" target="_blank" rel="noopener">与<em>NME</em>有关专辑的讲话</a>时说：“我会说，这将非常过分，非常戏剧性，非常戏剧性。绝对是个人的。这是关于活着的戏剧。特别是在这种情况下。”</p><p>他还讨论了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/maneskins-damiano-david-announces-solo-project-everywhere-3792250">他去年进入自己的独奏作品时分享的预告片视频剪辑，</a>他说：“我在世界各地旅行寻找我的声音，最终到达一切开始的地方”。当被问及这条线是否仅与他的单个“银线”有关，歌手回答：“不，这在人类层面上更个人化。在过去的几年中，我们工作了很多，我开始失去重点。我开始珍视对我来说并不是很有价值的东西。我基本上让自己不开心，而且我在做得很好。</p><p> “这一旅程是要减少所有过剩的旅程，而一切都不是我的幸福和满足感所需的100％。对我来说，这是更外部的，被弹出的想法。我被抓住了。我不得不为自己做很多工作，才能找到自己的身份。”</p><p>这位意大利艺术家将于今年晚些时候<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-maneskins-damiano-david-play-first-solo-gig-in-new-york-3807672">在今年晚些时候在纽约举行了独奏</a>。最初的巡回演出公告后，由于“惊人的需求”，添加了更多日期。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="达米亚诺·戴维（Damiano David） - 明年夏天（官方视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/EFqvVSqh6R8?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>大卫<a href="https://x.com/daviddamiano99/status/1877052771515425186" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在社交媒体上写道</a>：“到目前为止，您对这次旅行的回应感到震惊。我迫不及待想明年与你们一起唱歌和跳舞。”请参阅下面的所有旅行日期，然后<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fdamiano-david-tickets%2Fartist%2F5496724" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>访问英国门票，并<a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Fdamiano-david-tickets%2Fartist%2F3293004" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>购买美国门票。</p><h3><strong>达米亚诺·戴维（Damiano David）的2025年独奏世界巡回演唱会是：</strong></h3><p><strong>九月</strong><br /><strong>11  - 波兰，华沙 -  Cos Torwar</strong><br /> <strong>13  - 德国，柏林 -  Uber Eats音乐厅</strong><br /><strong>15  - 荷兰，阿姆斯特丹 -  Afas Live</strong><br /> <strong>17  - 德国，科隆 - 钯金</strong><br /><strong>21  - 西班牙，巴塞罗那 - 圣乔迪俱乐部</strong><br /><strong>22  - 西班牙，马德里 - 维津克中心</strong><br /><strong>26  - 法国，巴黎 - 阿迪达斯竞技场</strong><br /><strong>28  - 英国，伦敦 - 回报室<br />29 – UK, London – Roundhouse</strong></p><p><strong>十月</strong><br /><strong>2 – Belgium, Brussels – Forest National Club</str