我很忙！” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="The Cast &amp; Crew of &#039;The Rivals of Amziah King&#039; in the SXSW Studio with Reece Feldman" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/3IQcUlhazUM?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> The star also talked about the unexpected blending of genres in the film. “It&#39;s also kind of a musical!”他解释说。 “I didn&#39;t know it was going to be such a musical until I saw it”.</p><p> Despite not starring in a film for six years, Matthew McConaughey has been keeping himself busy. As well as writing his memoir, <em>Greenlights</em> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/matthew-mcconaughey-pitches-charli-xcx-in-boardroom-for-uber-eats-super-bowl-advert-3834729">he appeared in a commercial for Uber Eats</a> alongside <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/charli-xcx">Charli XCX</a> and <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/greta-gerwig">Greta Gerwig</a> during this year&#39;s Super Bowl.</p><p> Last year, he also said <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/matthew-mcconaughey-says-hes-thinking-about-running-for-political-office-3775569">he was considering running for political office</a> , after he seriously considered a run to be Texas governor in 2021.</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/matthew-mcconaugheys-big-film-return-gets-standing-ovation-at-sxsw-3845410">Matthew McConaughey&#39;s big film return gets standing ovation at SXSW</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
